    "Slide '3' up.",
    "The board is now [[2, 1, 3], [6, 7, 0], [5, 4, 8]].",
    "The '3' is now in its final position. 7.",
    "Now I will work on getting '1' and '2' into position without disturbing '3'.",
    "I slide '7' right, then '4' up, then '5' right, then '6' down."
